alluxio.client.block.stream

Class BlockOutStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.FilterOutputStream
        • alluxio.client.block.stream.BlockOutStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BoundedStream, Cancelable, Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class BlockOutStream
extends FilterOutputStream
implements BoundedStream, Cancelable
    Provides a stream API to write a block to Alluxio. An instance of this class can be obtained by calling AlluxioBlockStore.getOutStream(long, long, OutStreamOptions).
